{"tid":1691291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"檢測及認證業公海群上線","createTime":"2019-11-03T15:08:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T17:04:04.000Z","uid":289801,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"31d792c9f05689ba7e9d970e8745a2a6e084c348","tid":1691291,"uid":289801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:08:56.000Z","msg":"根據政府資料，檢測及認證業內有820家機構，僱員總數約18,280名。(2017年數字)<br />\n<br />\n萬八人 話多唔多 話少唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好睇小自己既力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其testing lab罷到工<br />\n不知攬炒到幾多trading既貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地亦已經無話罷工好難既本錢了<br />\n前線手足無一個就係一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞罷工要宣傳 要準備 要時間<br />\n大戰時刻隨時到 <br />\n各行各業既工會一定要係之前準備好<br />\n下一次罷工唔能夠再令佢地失望！<br />\n香港人 反抗呀！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n誠邀各位同行手足加入檢測及認證業公海<br />\n齊推罷工 籌組工會 <br />\n暫時仲係小貓三四隻 <br />\n靠大家幫手forward比你識既同事/朋友/舊同學啦！<br />\n<br />\n檢測及認證業同路人公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HKTestingnCertification\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKTestingnCertification&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axODT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=26cb232c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKTestingnCertification</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n感謝感謝"},{"pid":"6119a61fd3e62192bcba97d813bce3b1411002a2","tid":1691291,"uid":289801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:09:26.000Z","msg":"自推十連 香港人反抗"},{"pid":"f649b14b5936589bfa128c514b52da08cf3551c7","tid":1691291,"uid":289801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:10:01.000Z","msg":"自推十連 選個區選人耳仔都無埋痴孖筋"},{"pid":"ecbc3bf1653c7ffa9ca08bf5a1ece35c97e7a1f7","tid":1691291,"uid":289801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:10:41.000Z","msg":"自推十連 依個世界痴q左線"},{"pid":"8a4c326934233208d83131c26979daa85bef2f63","tid":1691291,"uid":289801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:10:54.000Z","msg":"自推十連 但聽日仲要返工"},{"pid":"c2389665a13c1d07662dedb707f169a751d4b66c","tid":1691291,"uid":289801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:11:27.000Z","msg":"自推十連 為左可以令依個痴q線既賺錢機器停低"},{"pid":"b9b903b1f3afe0f797eaa8a04b66fcc0b96098ba","tid":1691291,"uid":289801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:11:50.000Z","msg":"自推十連 以後唔洗再做佢既幫兇"},{"pid":"52255a7625f7a944d8d0962b6a7838b5ed2a44d3","tid":1691291,"uid":289801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:12:15.000Z","msg":"自推十連 要係大戰之前準備好"},{"pid":"7b8ad23392b5a5c0a7392ebafde556aa66cafbc7","tid":1691291,"uid":289801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:12:31.000Z","msg":"自推十連 智利都罷到工"},{"pid":"c8e500ef4199e0dba411d25769f9b649784dc0e7","tid":1691291,"uid":289801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:12:47.000Z","msg":"自推十連 點解我地唔得"},{"pid":"4968e2efbe70bc59b3abfa2d887458be5109bffb","tid":1691291,"uid":289801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:13:04.000Z","msg":"自推十連 唔好淨係講香港人奴性重"},{"pid":"ae40b127a621b151664376a345248465e89e74a2","tid":1691291,"uid":289801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:13:37.000Z","msg":"自推十連 唔通難就可以唔做？ 前線已經少一個就係無一個啦"},{"pid":"f8dfeaf8c8236642d93f8b2907e98a5cda845d82","tid":1691291,"uid":289801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:13:57.000Z","msg":"自推十連 和理非最有用既時候到了"},{"pid":"127bd840d6d6dd73e4eb09c4addf9ac5496a74ec","tid":1691291,"uid":289801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited